node.text:
#CircuitBreakerSg Day 47! Took a rest this evening and ordered Dim Sum for dinner from #TimHoWan through #deliveroosg! 😋Tried something new today. The seasame ball with salted egg yolk sauce and HK milk tea are all quite nice! Btw THW has some pretty good deal going on like the baked bun and congee are Buy 1 get 2nd at $2 only. #justsharing #notsponsored

#wentakeout #may2020 #sgig #sgfoodie #instafood #instadinner #dimsum #thwsg #familiarfood #dimsumathome #sgunited #sgfooddelivery #stayhomestaysafe
@sg_foodhopper they do island wide delivery. Check out their page
Would definitely order but they dont deliver to my area 😭
Exchange your old money at good rate,all you need is to PM me if you have any old Malaysia , Singapore, Kuwait, UAE , Brunei money for sell .. we deal with honesty
